#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.23:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Gahapativagga"
msgstr "3. Householders"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 23. Paṭhamahatthakasutta → hatthakāḷavakasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Paṭhamahatthakasutta"
msgstr "23. With Hatthaka (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.217"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā āḷaviyaṃ viharati aggāḷave cetiye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Āḷavī, at the Aggāḷava Tree-shrine."

msgctxt "an8.23:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.3"
msgid ""
"“sattahi, bhikkhave, acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgataṃ hatthakaṃ "
"āḷavakaṃ dhāretha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, you should remember the householder Hatthaka of Āḷavī as "
"someone who has seven amazing and incredible qualities."

msgctxt "an8.23:1.4"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.5"
msgid "Saddho hi, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "He’s faithful,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.6"
msgid "sīlavā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "ethical,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.7"
msgid "hirīmā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "conscientious,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.8"
msgid "ottappī, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "prudent,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.9"
msgid "bahussuto, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "learned,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.10"
msgid "cāgavā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "generous,"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.11"
msgid "paññavā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako—"
msgstr "and wise."

msgctxt "an8.23:1.12"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgataṃ "
"hatthakaṃ āḷavakaṃ dhārethā”ti."
msgstr ""
"You should remember the householder Hatthaka of Āḷavī as someone who has "
"these seven amazing and incredible qualities.”"

msgctxt "an8.23:1.13"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "an8.23:1.14"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ pāvisi."
msgstr ""
"When he had spoken, the Holy One got up from his seat and entered his "
"dwelling."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"hatthakassa āḷavakassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane "
"nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then a certain mendicant robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, went to the home of the householder Hatthaka of Āḷavī, where he sat on "
"the seat spread out."

msgctxt "an8.23:2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho hatthako āḷavako yena so bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā taṃ "
"bhikkhuṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho hatthakaṃ "
"āḷavakaṃ so bhikkhu etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Hatthaka went up to that mendicant, bowed, and sat down to one side. "
"The mendicant said to Hatthaka:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattahi kho tvaṃ, āvuso, acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, the Buddha declared that you have seven amazing and incredible "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an8.23:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.3"
msgid "‘Saddho, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr "He said that you’re faithful,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.4"
msgid "sīlavā … pe …"
msgstr "ethical,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.5"
msgid "hirīmā …"
msgstr "conscientious,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.6"
msgid "ottappī …"
msgstr "prudent,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.7"
msgid "bahussuto …"
msgstr "learned,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.8"
msgid "cāgavā …"
msgstr "generous,"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.9"
msgid "paññavā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako’ti."
msgstr "and wise."

msgctxt "an8.23:3.10"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho tvaṃ, āvuso, sattahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato”ti."
msgstr ""
"The Buddha declared that you have these seven amazing and incredible "
"qualities.”"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.11"
msgid "“Kaccittha, bhante, na koci gihī ahosi odātavasano”ti?"
msgstr "“But sir, I trust that no white-clothed lay people were present?”"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.12"
msgid "“Na hettha, āvuso, koci gihī ahosi odātavasano”ti."
msgstr "“No, there weren’t any white-clothed lay people present.”"

msgctxt "an8.23:3.13"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhante, yadettha na koci gihī ahosi odātavasano”ti."
msgstr "“That’s good, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.218"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so bhikkhu hatthakassa āḷavakassa nivesane piṇḍapātaṃ gahetvā "
"uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then that mendicant, after taking alms-food in Hatthaka of Āḷavī’s home, got "
"up from his seat and left."

msgctxt "an8.23:4.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so bhikkhu pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then after the meal, on his return from alms-round, he went to the Buddha, "
"bowed, sat down to one side, and told him of what he had discussed with the "
"householder Hatthaka. The Buddha said:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"hatthakassa āḷavakassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte "
"āsane nisīdiṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhante, hatthako āḷavako yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, hatthakaṃ āḷavakaṃ etadavacaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.4"
msgid ""
"‘sattahi kho tvaṃ, āvuso, acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.5"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.6"
msgid "Saddho, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavako;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.7"
msgid "sīlavā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.8"
msgid "hirīmā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.9"
msgid "ottappī …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.10"
msgid "bahussuto …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.11"
msgid "cāgavā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.12"
msgid "paññavā, bhikkhave, hatthako āḷavakoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:5.13"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho tvaṃ, āvuso, sattahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:6.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhante, hatthako maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:6.2"
msgid "‘kaccittha, bhante, na koci gihī ahosi odātavasano’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:6.3"
msgid "‘Na hettha, āvuso, koci gihī ahosi odātavasano’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.23:6.4"
msgid "‘Sādhu, bhante, yadettha na koci gihī ahosi odātavasano’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.23:7.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu."
msgstr "“Good, good, monk!"

msgctxt "an8.23:7.2"
msgid "Appiccho so, bhikkhu, kulaputto."
msgstr "That son of a good family has few wishes."

#. VAR: ñāyamāne → paññāpayamāne (mr)
msgctxt "an8.23:7.3"
msgid "Santeyeva attani kusaladhamme na icchati parehi ñāyamāne."
msgstr "He doesn’t want his own good qualities to be made known to others."

msgctxt "an8.23:7.4"
msgid ""
"Tena hi tvaṃ, bhikkhu, imināpi aṭṭhamena acchariyena abbhutena dhammena "
"samannāgataṃ hatthakaṃ āḷavakaṃ dhārehi, yadidaṃ appicchatāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Well then, mendicant, you should remember the householder Hatthaka of Āḷavī "
"as someone who has this eighth amazing and incredible quality, that is, "
"fewness of wishes.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.23:7.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
